## Root Causes (to be fixed in Phase 2b)

1. **`parse-markdown-to-blocks.ts`**: emits `paragraph('')` for each blank line and emits `paragraph('')` fallback for empty string. Must coalesce blank lines and return `Ok([])` for whitespace-only input.

2. **`hydrate-feed.ts`**: routes `hydrateNote` Err results to `step3CorruptedFiles` instead of throwing `Error('hydrateNote-invariant-violation: <filePath>: <reason>')`.

3. **`hydrate-note.ts`**: filters `paragraph('')` blocks and reassigns BlockIds after filtering. Must be a pure pass-through — no filtering, no ID reassignment. The parser contract (PROP-031) owns blank-line coalescing.

